## Frontend (Vite)
# If empty, the frontend will call `/api/*` on the same origin.
# In dev, Vite proxies `/api` to `http://localhost:5050` (see `vite.config.js`).
VITE_API_BASE_URL=

## Ask my CV agent endpoint (Tier 3)
# Leave empty to use the local fallback (no LLM, keyword-based).
# Set to your deployed Express endpoint (e.g. /api/ask) to enable real OpenAI.
# Example for dev: VITE_AI_ENDPOINT=/api/ask
VITE_AI_ENDPOINT=
